- Daniel H. Pink, *Drive* – on autonomy, mastery, and purpose as sources of motivation.
- Marcus Buckingham & Donald O. Clifton, *Now, Discover Your Strengths* – on strengths-based work and fulfillment.
- Manager Tools, *The Effective Manager* and related podcasts – practical tools for feedback, coaching, and delegation.

